SCP SL Specifics:
  Added a new Custom Role Ability:
    Custom Role Escape:
      This allows for a Custom Role that escapes to be guaranteed to be given another Custom Role
  Custom Roles that obtained this ability:
    Biochemist:
      Regular Escape: MTF Demolistionist
      Detained Escape: Explosive Chaos
    MTF Demolistionist:
      Detained Escape: Explosive Chaos
    Explosive Chaos:
      Detained Escape: MTF Demolistionist

  All Custom Roles now indicate if the abilities they have in the player console [~].
  Example:
    Biochemist:
    Explode on Death [Passive]
    Custom Role Escape [Passive]
    Healing Mist [Active]
